features-customize-customize-your-firefox = Pas jo { -brand-name-firefox }-browser oan
# HTML page description
features-customize-choose-how-your-browser-looks = Kies hoe’t jo browser derút sjocht mei tûzenen fergeze tema’s.
features-customize-firefox-themes-let-you-change = Mei { -brand-name-firefox }-tema's kinne jo it uterlik fan jo browser wizigje. Se stelle it kleureskema yn foar browsermenu’s en { -brand-name-firefox }-systeemsiden, en kinne sels in eftergrûnôfbylding tafoegje oan jo { -brand-name-firefox }-arkbalke.
features-customize-firefox-comes-with-a-default = { -brand-name-firefox } komt mei in standert systeemtema en is foarsjoen mei ljochte, tsjustere en kleurige fariaasjes.
# Used as accessible alternative text for an image
features-customize-image-of-the-default-themes = Ofbylding fan de standerttema’s dy’t by { -brand-name-firefox } levere wurde, mei ljochte, tsjustere en kleurige fariaasjes.
# Variables:
#   $amo (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/themes/
#   $top (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/search/?sort=rating&type=statictheme
#   $trending (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/search/?sort=hotness&type=statictheme
#   $recommended (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/search/?promoted=recommended&sort=random&type=statictheme
#   $music (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/themes/category/music/
#   $seasonal (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/themes/category/seasonal/
#   $sports (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/themes/category/sports/
#   $nature (url) - link to https://addons.mozilla.org/firefox/themes/category/nature/
features-customize-you-can-find-more-free-custom-v2 = Jo kinne mear fergeze oanpaste tema’s fine op <a { $amo }>addons.mozilla.org</a>. Blêdzje troch de <a { $top }>bêst beoardiele</a>, <a { $trending }>trending</a> en <a { $recommended }>meast oanrekommandearre</a> tema’s. Of sykje nei tema’s per kategory, ynklusyf <a { $music }>muzyk</a>, <a { $seasonal }>seizoen</a>, <a { $sports }>sport</a>, en <a { $nature } >natuer</a>. Pas jo ûnderfining oan nei jo smaak. Aardige bisten, kweade robots, prachtige lânskippen: der binne tûzenen opsjes om { -brand-name-firefox } jo eigen te meitsjen.
# Used as accessible alternative text for an image
features-customize-image-of-three-custom-firefox = Ofbylding fan trije oanpaste { -brand-name-firefox }-tema’s: in donkerpears en rôze tema mei wyt en oranje aksinten, in ljochtbêzje tema mei in akwarel fan fûgels en kersebloesems, en in donker swart en grien tema mei in hightech circuit patroan.
